We’ve teamed up with Jimmy’s Corner- a true neighborhood boxing bar- to create a limited series Corner Jacket. Founded by hall-of-fame cornerman, Jimmy Glenn, Jimmy’s Corner is a core representation of the NY boxing community that we seek to support and amplify. This limited edition, silk-lined corner jacket with silver boxing glove zipper pull features embroidered details that honor the legendary New York establishment.

100% of sales of the Everlast x Jimmy's Corner Corner Jacket will benefit the bar.

The collaboration is to be launched on August 18th, 2022, officially commemorated as Jimmy Glenn Day by the city of New York.
